{"title":"麦收时节","authors":["刘昌庆"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":6,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘昌庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星空下  磨镰声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由远而近在夜色中扩散"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声语重心长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我乡间的父老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脊梁弯成镰刀的角度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将命运的韧性表达得无比充分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们用手将水与月光洒在磨石上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一摇一晃地磨砺着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁色，从镰刀的怀抱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐次亮了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎忘记了外部的世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨镰人一脸庄重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地用大拇指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻试探着钢铁最冷峻的部分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不懂得什么是哲理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但知道磨刀不误砍柴工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锋利了才能披荆斩棘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早些把饱满的农事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获回家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个麦香浓郁的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲　镰刀　水　磨石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构成的一幅幅画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉淀在我童年的记忆中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割着我的思乡之情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多年之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走入城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借助这一幅幅画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孩子讲“粒粒皆辛苦”的道理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他懂了"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}